0x7242F8B741CE1086// NetworkIsNetworkIdAClone
BOOL _NETWORK_IS_NETWORK_ID_A_CLONE(int netId);Parameters:netId: The network id for an object or entity.Returns: Probably a bool, returns 1 if you don't have control over the netId entity.Returns true if the specified network id is controlled by someone else.
